Atom  HASP     0     3.6    0.1    110     no
Atom  CTR     -1     2.0    0.1    16      no
Atom  HCTR     0     2.0    0.1    16      no
Atom  GLU     -1     3.8    0.1    122     no
Atom  HGLU     0     3.8    0.1    122     no
Atom  HIS      0     3.9    0.1    130     no
Atom  HHIS     1     3.9    0.1    130     no
